data.description: A very rare find! Beautiful tree covered 3.42+/- acres in a gated community. Peaceful and private, yet within 5+/- miles of Lake Buchanan and Lake LBJ. 1.92 acres is Agricultural Land with very low taxes. Well for watering and 1957sqft +/- home, 4th bedroom makes a great office. 18x20 metal storage building with rollup door. Fiberglass sheets 5' down around the home to protect the slab from the tree roots. Must see! Easy to show, short drive to Austin or San Antonio. Seller is an elderly gentleman and would love a 14 day lease back, if possible.
